Bug.WithStack:
Build id: I20050923-1000

1. Have this file:

---
package p;

import java.util.ArrayList;
import java.util.List;

public class Foo {
	
	static final List<String> x = new ArrayList<String>();
	{
		x.clear();
	}

}
---

2. Inline x.

Observe: Both imports have been removed.
'Delete constant declaration' needs to be enabled.

